<plot>"Mind-Games" is a short film set in a three bedroom house. Adam Connors is a 17 year old who is afraid of the dark and being alone at night. All his life Adam has slept with his light on and bedroom door open. When Adam's parents go away for the night, he arranges to have a friend come over and stay the night with him. But when his friend lets him down Adam's mind begins to play games with him. Will Adam learn to control his fear or will the fear control him?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?370606</url></doc>
